  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the vast universe, pilot your spaceship to chase green stars! Each star you collect adds to your total score. Challenge yourself and aim for a new high score!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Controls:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use <strong>W, A, S, D</strong> to move the spaceship</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Press <strong>Q, E</strong> to rotate the spaceship</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Realistic space experience:</strong> Explore a boundless starry sky with dazzling stars</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Immersive music:</strong> Enjoy beautiful melodies in the solitude of the cosmos</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Relaxing gameplay:</strong> Experience ultimate relaxation for the price of a drink</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join this breathtaking interstellar adventure now!</p>",
